videos.description: With time running out in the first half, Memphis' Boogie Ellis comes up with a steal and banks in a half-court shot at the buzzer.

videos.description: After Saint Mary's got out to an 8-0 lead, Memphis' D.J. Jeffries checks into the game but mistakenly has his jersey on backwards.
